#Find out how many days,weeks,months,we have left;if we live untill 90 years old
#input : Your current age
#output : You have a days , b weeks , c months left
#Assume : 1 year=365 days,1 year=52 weeks,1 year=12 months

age=int(input("Enter your age:"))
years_left=90-age
days_left=years_left*365
months_left=years_left*12
weeks_left=years_left*52
print(f"You have {days_left} days, {weeks_left} weeks,{months_left} months left.")

